OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt was interesting to read a claim on a
OL,7,Fforum that it was a surprise that
OL,8,FBritish TV still had announcers.
OL,10,FIt is never a bad thing to question
OL,11,Fconventions. Sometimes things are
OL,12,Fsimply done through habit or tradition.
OL,14,FThis week ITV 1 reintroduced idents
OL,15,Fbefore their key morning programmes.
OL,16,FHowever the idents are voiced by
OL,17,Fprogramme presenters ` not announcers.
