OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FMost TV channels in the UK and Ireland
OL,7,Ffollow the same convention ` an ident
OL,8,Fwith a voiceover (either live or
OL,9,Frecorded) precedes virtually all
OL,10,Fprogrammes.
OL,12,FOf course, this is a relatively new
OL,13,Fconvention which was an evolution of
OL,14,Fthe standard BBC practice in the 60s
OL,15,Fand 70s.
OL,17,FIt was not unusual on ITV back then to
OL,18,Fgo straight from a trail or advert into
OL,19,Fthe pre-programme ident ` or frontcap `
OL,20,Fof the production company.
OL,23,EPub: 11-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
