OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FSo are announcers still needed today?
OL,8,FI'd argue that on the main public
OL,9,Fservice channels there should be no
OL,10,Fquestion over their fundamental value.
OL,12,FFirstly, a voiced ident is part of the
OL,13,Fchannel brand.
OL,15,FSome programmes benefit from a nicely
OL,16,Fscripted introduction.
OL,23,EPub: 11-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
