OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn the case of a channel like BBC One,
OL,7,Fthe feeling that a live announcer is
OL,8,Fwatching live with the audience helps
OL,9,Fto lift the channel above the others.
OL,10,FThe channel is a living, breathing,
OL,11,Freactive thing ` not a streamed video.
OL,13,FI also think that spoken announcements
OL,14,Fare the best way of ensuring Ofcom
OL,15,Fcompliance warnings are given.
OL,17,FYes, you can argue for captions or
OL,18,Fgeneric recorded announcements on
OL,19,Fviolence or strong language. But I
OL,20,Fprefer to hear them integrated into
OL,21,Fproperly scripted links.
OL,23,EPub: 11-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
