OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FOf course, I suppose I'm really arguing
OL,7,Fthat announcers are needed on the main
OL,8,FBBC channels. I can't pretend that the
OL,9,Fsame principled arguments should apply
OL,10,Fto all the other channels, especially
OL,11,Fthe smaller ones.
OL,13,FI've argued in the past that the range
OL,14,Fof voices used in modern BBC continuity
OL,15,Fmay have widened too much. I stand by
OL,16,Fthat. Diversity should not mean
OL,17,Fanything goes and undermines the role
OL,18,Fof skilled announcers with good voices
OL,19,Flike Duncan Newmarch.
OL,23,EPub: 11-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
