OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FI can also accept that having a live
OL,7,Fannouncer on duty at all times `
OL,8,Fincluding during Breakfast or the
OL,9,Fdaytime News Channel simulcast ` was
OL,10,Fwasteful.
OL,12,FPerhaps the efficiency in the BBC
OL,13,Fnations ` where the announcer is also
OL,14,Fthe transmission director ` should
OL,15,Foffer inspiration?
OL,17,FBut if anyone very seriously proposes
OL,18,Faxing announcers on the main BBC
OL,19,Fchannels, I'll happily join the fight
OL,20,Fto save them.
OL,23,EPub: 11-Jan-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
