OL,3,GOPINIONCLive announcers: an essential
OL,4,Cpart of PSB channels
OL,5,
OL,6,FModern announcers are not the legacy of
OL,7,FSylvia Peters. They are an essential
OL,8,Fpart of the grammar of a public service
OL,9,Fbroadcaster.
OL,11,FIf you think otherwise, watch the mess
OL,12,Fthe next time you're on holiday in the
OL,13,FUSA.
